# Tic-Tac-Toe Game

A fully functional **Tic-Tac-Toe** game built using **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**.  
The game supports two players, detects winners, handles draw scenarios, and allows resetting or starting a new game at any time.

This project focuses on strengthening core JavaScript fundamentals such as DOM manipulation, event handling, and state management.

---

## Features

- Two-player gameplay (X vs O)
- Automatic winner detection
- Draw detection when all 9 cells are filled
- Prevents overwriting already selected cells
- Reset Game and New Game functionality
- Dynamic message display for winner and draw

---

